title: Can somebody explain this?
body:
https://clips.twitch.tv/AstuteSourSproutTBTacoLeft

I've watched this clip about six or seven times now, and I still have no idea how Fizz's ult connected with Irelia. Can anybody give me an insight into exactly what happened here?

replies.body:
{{sticker:sg-ahri-1}} 

Yeeeaaaaaa that's not really supposed to happen I don't believe. Post this over in the [**Report a Bug**](http://boards.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/bug-report) section to make sure the Devs catch it!!
